snippet.title: Zombie Wars gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Zombie Wars, PC game produced by Gee Whiz! Entertainment in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/zombie-wars/12188/
Playing a couple of levels of this interesting arcade platform game on the Halloween Harry style.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Adventures of Lomax - https://youtu.be/AAfzYjowuxU
Mega Man X4 - https://youtu.be/BY_OSFH-j8k
Jazz Jackrabbit Holiday Hare 1995 - https://youtu.be/cSgFNzuDRVs
